Its from Colonial Cousins' third album 'Aatma'. It is the trademark fusion of Pop and Carnatic music.

Singers- Colonial Cousins and Yachna

Lyricist- Lesle Lewis

Instrumentalists- Zoheb-Keyboard, Darshan-Drums, Nyzel-Electric Guitar, Dibyajyoti-Bass Guitar, Sanjoy-accoustic guitar, Arun-Percussion

Backing Vocalists- Shannon Donald, Shawna Dsouza, Crystal Sequeira 

Music conceived and created by Lesle Lewis (www.leslelewis.com)


Lyrics:
(Lesle)
Looking into those 
angel eyes 
Searching for the love endlessly....

(Yachna)
Main aapse mohabbat karti hu

(Lesle)
Suddenly I realize 
There's more to you that eyes cannot see

(Yachna)
Sach bahut mohabbat karti hu

(Lesle)
Something deep inside my soul ... 
Tells me you are the one I was looking for....

(Yachna)
Khoyi rehti hamesha bus aapke liye

(Lesle)
Sunder si hai balma

(Hariharan)
Sunder balma man baave
reee... Aeeeeee eee 
sunder balma man baave

Sunder balma man bhaave re.....

Mujhe uljhan mein dal kar kaha gaye aap

Touch you in the deepest hour..
